{"tid":2227802,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓團25歲比利時成員惹關注　獲讚似荷里活明星","createTime":"2020-10-03T05:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T03:08:01.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"0fca6705ba08a3b0403aaccb2515e7799130b853","tid":2227802,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:39:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20201003/photo/bkn-20201003102050242-1003_00862_001_01p.jpg?20201003103558\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20201003%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201003102050242-1003_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20201003103558&h=3ce753c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來自比利時的Black Swan成員Fatou惹起網民關注。<br />\n<br />\n韓國演藝界每年都有不少組合誕生，而出道在即的韓國女團Black Swan，除了有韓籍成員，還有來自日本、巴西及比利時，希望以多國籍成員在樂壇闖出名堂。而出道前，隊中出生於塞內加爾的25歲比利時成員Fatou便成功惹起網民關注，為出道製造話題。<br />\n<br />\n官方簡稱為B.S的Black Swan是韓國DR Music旗下經過重組的5人女團，成員包括同門女團RaNia出身的惠美、瑛欣及Leia，再加入兩位新成員Fatou與Judy。身高1米73擁有模特兒身材的Fatou，今年7月在組合官方社交網以韓文親筆信留言自我介紹，透露自己於塞內加爾出生，並於比利時成長，現在則於韓國生活，又謂正與隊友努力準備出道，希望可以獲得大家的愛與支持。不少網民大讚Fatou十足荷里活明星一樣靚女，是隊中最美成員，而她在成為練習生之前，亦曾從事模特兒工作。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7e63bb463bcf9566bb0cc55664d5146f8586b5","tid":2227802,"uid":48783,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:40:43.000Z","msg":"係黑人都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"1408f3c40de3a3431d46470234c1791b3d5034c5","tid":2227802,"uid":377617,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:41:39.000Z","msg":"好怪...